	var fileName = request.pathParams.file;
	var currentRecord = "0624648647622110ed23d264336d4338";
	var ar = new GlideRecord('sys_attachment');
	ar.addQuery('table_sys_id', currentRecord);
	ar.addQuery('file_name', fileName);
	ar.query();
	
	if (fileName.indexOf('-svg')>0) {
		response.setContentType('image/svg+xml');
	}
	else{
		response.setContentType('image/jpeg');
	}
	
	response.setStatus(200);

	if (ar.next()) {
		var gsa = new GlideSysAttachment();
		var attachmentStream = new gsa.getContentStream(ar.sys_id.toString()); 
		var writer = response.getStreamWriter();
		writer.writeStream(attachmentStream);
	} else {
		return "file not found";
	}

})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_727158_gw_react/container/img/{file}</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/img/{file}</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>false</requires_authentication><requires_snc_internal_role>true</requires_snc_internal_role><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2023-05-03 02:28:44</sys_created_on><sys_id>0624648647622110ed23d264336d4338</sys_id><sys_mod_count>7</sys_mod_count><sys_name>IMG</sys_name><sys_package display_value="GW React" source="x_727158_gw_react">0cee500247622110ed23d264336d4392</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="GW React">0cee500247622110ed23d264336d4392</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_0624648647622110ed23d264336d4338</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2023-05-08 22:52:33</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="React app container">4a4f58c247622110ed23d264336d43d8</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>
